50|$|A {{referendum}} on the <b>electoral</b> <b>law</b> was held in San Marino on 22 September 1996. Voters were asked four questions on changes to the <b>electoral</b> <b>law</b> and <b>electoral</b> system, {{all of which were}} approved by voters.|$|R
